                            <comment id="13490743" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Mon, 5 Nov 2012 17:15:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Olivier. I&apos;m still running Lion. It probably won&apos;t make a difference but at least you&apos;ve given me one more excuse to do the upgrade! Hopefully the locale won&apos;t make a difference for this error.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13490746" author="olamy" created="Mon, 5 Nov 2012 17:18:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;hehe &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; (that&apos;s just the output of mvn -v)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you have enough informations to reproduce ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13490752" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Mon, 5 Nov 2012 17:21:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I think so.  However, I checked in a fix that should at least avoid the NPE. However, it will probably result in just using the default LoggerContext, which for Maven is probably OK.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13491377" author="olamy" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2012 10:55:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Tested and works fine. I will test &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-105&quot; title=&quot;Change level name String&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-105&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-105&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; next week (vacations now &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; )&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
